NAME
    Test::TypeConstraints - testing value with Data::Validator like
    validation.

SYNOPSIS
      use Test::TypeConstraints;

      Test::TypeConstraints::type_is_a_ok($got, "ArrayRef[Int]", "type should be ArrayRef[Int]");

DESCRIPTION
    Test::TypeConstraints is for testing type check with Data::Validator
    like validation.

AUTHOR
    Keiji Yoshimi <walf443 at gmail dot com>

SEE ALSO
    +<Data::Validator>, +<Mouse::Util::TypeConstraints>

